arsh%20GA%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139821012896160" co-class="co-affbox">Glenn A. Marsh</a>,<sup>\n1\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Smith%20C%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139821014821120" co-class="co-affbox">Craig Smith</a>,<sup>\n2\n,</sup><sup>\n4\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Tachedjian%20M%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139821014320880" co-class="co-affbox">Mary Tachedjian</a>,<sup>\n1\n,</sup><sup>\n2\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=De%20Jong%20C%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139821014817296" co-class="co-affbox">Carol De Jong</a>,<sup>\n2\n,</sup><sup>\n4\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Virtue%20ER%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139821013656880" co-class="co-affbox">Elena R. Virtue</a>,<sup>\n1\n,</sup><sup>\n2\n,</sup><sup>\n5\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Yu%20M%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139821013759584" co-class="co-affbox">Meng Yu</a>,<sup>\n1\n,</sup><sup>\n2\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Bulach%20D%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139821086400096" co-class="co-affbox">Dieter Bulach</a>,<sup>\n1\n,</sup><sup>\n2\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Liu%20JP%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139821087916304" co-class="co-affbox">Jun-Ping Liu</a>,<sup>\n6\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Michalski%20WP%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139821012575472" co-class="co-affbox">Wojtek P. Michalski</a>,<sup>\n1\n,</sup><sup>\n3\n</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Middleton%20D%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20011515" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm13982104100