33.</span> <span class="nowrap">[<a class="int-reflink" href="/pmc/articles/PMC2626820/">PMC free article</a>]</span> [<a href="/pubmed/8903153" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2788226&amp;issue-id=182901&amp;journal-id=440&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Emerg+Infect+Dis&amp;title=A+novel+morbillivirus+pneumonia+of+horses+and+its+transmission+to+humans.&amp;author=K+Murray&amp;author=R+Rogers&amp;author=L+Selvey&amp;author=P+Selleck&amp;author=A+Hyatt&amp;volume=1&amp;publication_year=1995&amp;pages=31-33&amp;pmid=8903153&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2788226&amp;issue-id=182901&amp;journal-id=440&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="pone.0008266-Li1">4. <span class="element-citation">Li W, Shi Z, Yu M, Ren W, Smith C, et al.  Bats are natural reservoirs of SARS-like coronaviruses. <span><span class="ref-journal">Science. </span>2005;<span class="ref-vol">310</span>:676\xe2\x80\x93679.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/16195424" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2788226&amp;issue-id=182901&amp;journal-id=440&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Science&amp;title=Bats+are+natural+reservoirs+of+SARS-like+coronaviruses.&amp;author=W+Li&amp;author=Z+Shi&amp;author=M+Yu&amp;author=W+Ren&amp;author=C+Smith&amp;volume=310&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;pages=676-679&amp;pmid=16195424&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2788226&amp;issue-id=182901&amp;journal-id=440&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="pone.0